snippet.title: ComicBookCast2
snippet.description:
The Comic Book Cast is an online geek culture community. Our mission is to deliver daily news in a easy to understand to the point video format along with our weekly podcasts an discussions that helps you embrace Marvel & DC Films that we all love in a unique way and having a few good laughs in-between. We are dedicated to giving you honest opinions, analytical discussions, and more.

If you like what we do you can check out the bonus membership where we offer even audio commentaries, gaming videos, bonus discussions and more.
